	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Honestly, I don't want to get flamed for this, but I am a wizard, and doing 1000dmg at lvl 49, and then our lvl 60 spell sunstrike does only 1600dd,and plus it is a fire spell, which is quite resisted, I ean it pretty much sucks.<br>I think somoene should start one of those petitions to Verant, unless one is already in progress, if i knew how to start one, I would, so if i could get maybe a site where this petition or future petition will be at, cuz damn, i'm signing.<br><br>Maybe they could put a spell that in the expansion after SoL, maybe a DD that does 1900-2000 magic, but keep sunstrike cuz it Could have it's uses:)<br><br>I'd like to hear your opinion about the subject<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;    THX ALOT</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
